程序包 model

类 AppointmentOutcomeRecord

Object
AppointmentOutcomeRecord
public class AppointmentOutcomeRecord extends Object
The AppointmentOutcomeRecord class represents an appointment outcome record, which is part of a Bill and an Appointment. It contains information about the outcome of a patient's appointment, like the date of the appointment and consultation notes.
